Features:

1. Get login authorization

User:
1. Follow a user
2. Unfollow a user

Listener
1. Creation of a new listener
2. Get listener details
3. Get all listeners

Artist
1. Creation of a new artist
2. Get artist details
3. Get all artists
4. Get image for a artist — later

Song
1. Get all songs
2. Get song by title
3. Get song by genre
4. Get song by album
5. Get song by artist
6. Like a song
7. Dislike a song
8. Mark song as favorite 
9. Increase views on a song

Album
1. Get album by title
2. Get image for a song — later

Playlist
1. Create a new playlist
2. Add song to a playlist
3. Increase views on a playlist
